    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "phase2_agent_t",
      "x": 80, "y": 355,
      "width": 540, "height": 100,
      "text": "Agent (DeepSeek-V3)\n\n拿到 Phase 1 三路结果 → 分析疑点 → 自主决定下一步\n\"文本+封面+帧都干净\" → done(approved)\n\"帧里有文字看不清\" → ocr_frames([2,4])  \"标题说听这段\" → transcribe_audio\n\"5帧不够\" → extract_more_frames(5, late)  \"证据不足\" → escalate(证据链)",
      "originalText": "Agent (DeepSeek-V3)\n\n拿到 Phase 1 三路结果 → 分析疑点 → 自主决定下一步\n\"文本+封面+帧都干净\" → done(approved)\n\"帧里有文字看不清\" → ocr_frames([2,4])  \"标题说听这段\" → transcribe_audio\n\"5帧不够\" → extract_more_frames(5, late)  \"证据不足\" → escalate(证据链)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
